oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Stonewall Jackson at the Salem Co Civic Center (0784)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jackson, Stonewall; Grand ole opry (Radio program);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Stonewall Jackson, Pattie Flores Show, Elmer Fudpucker, and Kathy Raye at the Salem Co. Civic Center on August 4. Poster features metal photoplates of Stonewall Jackson, Pattie Flores Show, Elmer Fudpucker, and Kathy Raye. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20742.
